# Anchored. Unanchored, `sage/` matches a directory named `sage` at ANY depth —
# it silently swallowed runtime/plugin-overlay/skills/sage/, the plugin's /sage
# router, which therefore never got committed. It existed on every developer's
# disk and in no clean checkout. Only a vendored copy at the repo root is meant
# to be ignored here.
/sage/
